Start Kafka

1) bin/zookeeper-server-start.sh config/zookeeper.properties
2) bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties

Create topic

3) bin/kafka-topics.sh --create --zookeeper localhost:2181 --replication-factor 1 --partitions 1 --topic salestopic

start hbase and create table

4) create 'salesdata', 'count'

Run the projects in IDE

5) Run the projects in Scala IDE

Note : Please follow the below steps to add the jars given in jar directory

1) Add metrics-core and google-collection jars to Final Project

2) Add jcommon and jfreechart jars to Visualization project


